---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import SectionContainer from '../components/common/SectionContainer.astro';
import Card from '../components/common/Card.astro';
import Button from '../components/common/Button.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="Engineering rigor meets security expertise. Learn about José Manuel Lizardi and Lizardi Consulting."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <SectionContainer class="pt-12">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl text-signal-white mb-4">
        About Lizardi Consulting
      </h1>
      <p class="text-intel-gray text-lg">
        Engineering rigor meets security expertise
      </p>
    </div>
  </SectionContainer>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <SectionContainer class="pb-12">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none">
        <p class="text-intel-gray text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Lizardi Consulting brings a unique blend of engineering discipline and security acumen to the consulting space. Founded by <strong class="text-signal-white">José Manuel Lizardi</strong>, the practice combines systematic engineering approaches with deep security expertise to deliver pragmatic, measurable solutions.
        </p>

        <p class="text-intel-gray text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
          With a background in Civil and Chemical Engineering, Business Administration, and hands-on experience at <strong class="text-signal-white">GE Vernova</strong> working on power plant systems, José brings a methodical approach to solving complex security challenges. This engineering foundation ensures that solutions are not just theoretically sound, but practically implementable.
        </p>

        <p class="text-intel-gray text-lg leading-relaxed mb-12">
          Currently pursuing <strong class="text-signal-white">IBM AI Engineering certification</strong>, the practice stays at the forefront of emerging technologies while maintaining a grounded, results-oriented philosophy. As an <strong class="text-signal-white">ISO 9001 Lead Auditor</strong>, quality and continuous improvement are built into every engagement.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </SectionContainer>

  <!-- Credentials -->
  <SectionContainer class="pb-12 bg-tactical-navy/20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="font-display text-3xl text-signal-white mb-8 text-center">
        Credentials & Experience
      </h2>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <!-- GE Vernova -->
        <Card>
          <div class="mb-3">
            <span class="text-electric-cyan text-xs font-mono">2022-2024</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-xl text-signal-white mb-3">
            GE Vernova
          </h3>
          <p class="text-intel-gray text-sm">
            Power plant systems engineering and operations. Worked on critical infrastructure systems requiring the highest levels of reliability and security.
          </p>
        </Card>

        <!-- IBM AI Engineering -->
        <Card>
          <div class="mb-3">
            <span class="text-intel-gold text-xs font-mono">IN PROGRESS</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-xl text-signal-white mb-3">
            IBM AI Engineering
          </h3>
          <p class="text-intel-gray text-sm">
            Professional certification in AI implementation and strategy. Focused on practical applications of AI in business contexts.
          </p>
        </Card>

        <!-- ISO 9001 -->
        <Card>
          <div class="mb-3">
            <span class="text-operational-green text-xs font-mono">CERTIFIED</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-xl text-signal-white mb-3">
            ISO 9001 Lead Auditor
          </h3>
          <p class="text-intel-gray text-sm">
            Quality management systems and process optimization. Ensures systematic, auditable approaches to all consulting work.
          </p>
        </Card>

        <!-- Education -->
        <Card>
          <div class="mb-3">
            <span class="text-electric-cyan text-xs font-mono">EDUCATION</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-xl text-signal-white mb-3">
            Engineering & Business
          </h3>
          <p class="text-intel-gray text-sm">
            Civil & Chemical Engineering, Business Administration. A multidisciplinary foundation for solving complex problems.
          </p>
        </Card>
      </div>
    </div>
  </SectionContainer>

  <!-- Philosophy -->
  <SectionContainer class="pb-12">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="font-display text-3xl text-signal-white mb-8 text-center">
        Consulting Philosophy
      </h2>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <Card>
          <h3 class="font-display text-lg text-signal-white mb-3">
            Engineering Rigor
          </h3>
          <p class="text-intel-gray text-sm">
            Every recommendation is backed by systematic analysis. No hand-waving, no buzzwords—just clear reasoning and measurable outcomes.
          </p>
        </Card>

        <Card>
          <h3 class="font-display text-lg text-signal-white mb-3">
            Pragmatic Implementation
          </h3>
          <p class="text-intel-gray text-sm">
            Solutions must work in the real world, with real constraints. Theoretical perfection that can't be executed is worthless.
          </p>
        </Card>

        <Card>
          <h3 class="font-display text-lg text-signal-white mb-3">
            Continuous Improvement
          </h3>
          <p class="text-intel-gray text-sm">
            Security and technology landscapes evolve constantly. ISO 9001 principles ensure we're always improving processes and outcomes.
          </p>
        </Card>
      </div>
    </div>
  </SectionContainer>

  <!-- Mercalitica -->
  <SectionContainer class="pb-24 bg-gunmetal/30">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="font-display text-3xl text-signal-white mb-6">
        Part of Mercalitica
      </h2>
      <p class="text-intel-gray mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Lizardi Consulting is part of <a href="https://www.mercalitica.mx/team" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-electric-cyan hover:underline">Mercalitica</a>, a collective of specialists providing integrated consulting services across technology, security, and business domains.
      </p>
      <Button href="/contact" size="lg">
        Start a Conversation
      </Button>
    </div>
  </SectionContainer>
</BaseLayout>
